OL,6,FThe Health and Safety Executive
OL,7,Fpublished the footage after its
OL,8,Fprosecution of a firm and three
OL,9,Findividuals
OL,11,FA mother who was hurled from a
OL,12,Ffairground ride has agreed a #1.43
OL,13,Fmillion settlement of a High Court
OL,14,Fclaim against the ride's owner.
