OL,6,FKhadra Ali spent weeks in a coma and
OL,7,Ffour months in hospital after she was
OL,8,Fejected from the Xcelerator ride at
OL,9,Fthe Funderpark funfair in Yiewsley,
OL,10,Fwest London, on April 10 2018, with
OL,11,Ffootage showing her flying through the
OL,12,Fair while the ride continued to rotate.
OL,14,FMs Ali sued Derek Hackett, the ride's
OL,15,Fowner trading as Hackett Fairs, for
OL,16,Fdamages after being left unable to do
OL,17,Fchores or activities with her children.
