OL,6,FIn May, the Health and Safety
OL,7,FExecutive (HSE) said she had suffered
OL,8,Fmultiple fractures to her back, hips,
OL,9,Fpelvis, ribs and both collarbones as
OL,10,Fwell as internal bleeding and a
OL,11,Fsignificant head injury.
OL,13,FA High Court hearing on Wednesday was
OL,14,Ftold that Ms Ali had reached an out-of-
OL,15,Fcourt settlement with Hackett, with
OL,16,Fher lawyer, Robert Kellar KC, claiming
OL,17,Fthe #1.43 million sum was "within the
OL,18,Frange of reasonable offers".
