OL,6,FJudge Rebecca Crane approved the sum
OL,7,Fat the end of the short hearing in
OL,8,FLondon, describing it as "a very
OL,9,Fsensible settlement for both parties".
OL,11,FThe HSE said earlier this year that Ms
OL,12,FAli, who is now in her 50s, was riding
OL,13,Fwith her daughter and had not been
OL,14,Fproperly restrained in her seat when
OL,15,Fshe was thrown from the ride.
OL,17,FShe "screamed for help" while on the
OL,18,F"fast-motion" ride and clung on before
OL,19,Fbeing ejected, hitting the barrier of
OL,20,Fthe next ride and landing on the
OL,21,Fground, the executive said.
