OL,6,FThe investigation also found that on
OL,7,Fthe day of the incident, Hackett's
OL,8,Fride operator had no attendant
OL,9,Fassisting them despite the operations
OL,10,Fmanual requiring a minimum of two
OL,11,Fpeople to operate and monitor the ride.
OL,13,FThe operator did not check each
OL,14,Frider's restraint bar as they should
OL,15,Fhave before starting the ride and did
OL,16,Fnot notice that Ms Ali required
OL,17,Fassistance and stop the ride.
