OL,6,FHackett, previously of School Street,
OL,7,FRadcliffe, Manchester, was one of
OL,8,Fthree men who admitted health and
OL,9,Fsafety offences at Westminster
OL,10,FMagistrates' Court earlier this year.
OL,12,FHe received an 18-week sentence,
OL,13,Fsuspended for 18 months, and was
OL,14,Fordered to pay #4,800 in costs.
